    @FunctionalInterface
public interface GenerateFn<A>
extends com.jnape.palatable.lambda.functions.Fn1<Seed,​Result<? extends Seed,​A>>
    A pure and referentially transparent function that converts a Seed to a Result. The same Seed will always yield the same Result, and all Seeds are guaranteed to return a result.
